    <h3 class="ui left aligned header">How it works:</h3>
    <div class="fifteen wide column">
      <div class="ui three column centered divided stackable grid">
        <div class="column">
          <p> Users list available tickets.</p>
          <p>Site visitors, and other users view available tickets.</p>
          <p> Users contact the ticket lister, by sending an email to: iwanttickets@ticketswapper.com </p>
          <p>TicketSwapper forwards to the Lister. The Lister responds directly to the inquirer via email.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="column">
          <p>Once an agreement is made, users forward the agreement to service@ticketswapper.com and transfer the tickets to service@ticketswapper.com.</p>
          <p>TicketSwapper receives each users transfers, and verifies that the tickets match the agreement.</p>
          <p>TicketSwapper does not accept transfers from either party until both transfers have arrived and are verified.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="column">
          <p>Once TicketSnapper has accepted both user-to-TicketSwapper transfers, TicketSwapper transfers each set of tickets to the new owner, and the transaction is complete.</p>
          <p> In the event that a user fails to transfer tickets to TicketSwapepr, TicketSwapper will not accept the other users transfer and will notify the user.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
