          <h3 class="ui blue center aligned header">What types of tickets work?</h3>
          <p>Most tickets purchased on Ticketmaster, or livenation are transferrable. Tickets for some Eventbrite events are also transferrable depending on whether the event organizer enabled the feature or not. Many college sporting events are also transferrable.</p>
          <p>TicketSwapper does not accept tickets by mail or physical tickets, to process transactions tickets must be electronically transferable. Send specific questions to service@ticketswapper.com. </p>
        </div>
        <div class="column">
          <h3 class="ui blue center aligned header">How do I check if my tickets are transferrable?</h3>
          <p> For Ticketmaster or livenation events log into the account you purchased your tickets. Visit the view all orders page, and look for the Transfer button to the right of the red My Tickets button.</p>
          TicketSwapper does not accept tickets by mail and does not allow transactions involving users mailing tickets to eachother.</p>
